Dialogue: Get back here, you!
I can't bear all this waiting around...
Plain sailing ahead!
I'd never shirk my duties as helmsman, but sometimes I do miss the days when it was just me and my rod.
Lucky for you I'm a fisher myself, so I know that slow and steady brings the bites.
Never fails to take your breath away, does it?
I'd best write today's log before I forget...
It's hard to keep a steady hand when the ocean's beauty is distracting me.
I must record every detail of the day's weather conditions. Tedious work, but it must be done.
Get your rods ready─here comes enough fish for the lot of you!
And we're here! Time to fish!
Looks like handsome hauls all around!
Oi, can you hear me? Hey! Ahoy there!
There's no mistaking this light─we've found ourselves a spectral current!
Ain't got no need for small fry, so I throw 'em right back to the sea.
Ye ain't gotta see a fish to know its size! Mark well how long it takes to bite, and how fiercely it pulls.
An expert angler's got two qualities: patience and a discernin' eye. Don't waste time pullin' minnows outta the sea.
One cast, one catch!
To catch a fish that's bein' conservative with its bites, you'll need to use your precision hookset.
If a fish is pullin' with the strength of an aurochs, you'll need a powerful hookset to match it.
If ye wanna get straight to fishin', spread some chum in the water and watch the fish crowd around!
Now do some fishin' of yer own!
Not every kind of bait will have fish chomping at your hook right away. However, patience is a virtue every fisher's got.
Rumor has it the bait they sell on the boat's what you want to use if it's the size of the catch you care about.
The ocean's full of hungry beasts all waiting for food to drop in front of their gullets─I've even seen shellfish at the end of some hooks!
Now take your fill of the ocean's bounty!
Look at this! We're above the clouds!
Wow! The sea of clouds puts the real sea to shame!
Come on, let's go play over there!
Where am I? ...Who am I?
This is unacceptable! Unacceptable, I tell you!
It's off to the hole with you.
No, please! Anythin' but that!
The king's will be done!
Yah!
The remaining benthos may struggle, bereft of leader...
Come now, she was maniacal.
If there were more guards, they would be here by now.
That was all of them? Every last one...?
'Tis a boon we find this sanctum intact.
We may at last turn our attention to investigation.
My name shall be inscribed in the pages of history!
Not if you stand around talking all day, it won't.
Ox'Dalan, grant me thy strength. And wisdom. And perhaps some extra luck wouldn't go amiss...
Surely, you have chiseled enough?
It's my turn!
No! I must continue chiseling!
Tradition dictates it!
Our ancestors would be proud!
No thanks to your incessant chiseling.
Scree!
So many tunnels and grottoes...
Scree! Scree!♪
And scree to you, my good sir! ...Or was it madam?
It says this is the way! ...I think.
\<huff> \<puff> Wait up, I say!
A warding talisman? How splendid!
Let the delving continue!
We are much obliged to the Night's Blessed.
The tunnels are full of shiny, sparkly ore!
We must better study how to care for the sick...
Ronkan moss is very valuable. We must conserve our supply.
Do you think the serpent will like this?
I must prepare a herbal soak!
The serpent will surely be pleased!
And one! And two!
\<whimper>
\<huff> \<huff> I can run...no more...
Take your ease until the next stela is complete.
The great serpent is pleased with our work. A rest is well deserved!
Scree! Scree!
Time for the next shift!
Come now, our replacements are here!
Patience! Just a little further, a little deeper!
These vegetables from Slitherbough are positively delectable!
We'll have a full stomach for a full day of mining ahead!
Scree...
Scree!
Scree! Scree!
S-Screeeeeeeee!
That cargo ain't gone through inspections yet. We got rules and regulations here─yer gonna have to put it back.
Where do ye want this?
Ye must be jokin'...
Urgh... The pain... I can't move an ilm or I'll...
Just...just leave the medicine here...and go...
Someone doesn't have their sea legs yet.
Don't give him any ideas...
Sailed every corner of the high seas, huh?
Goes down almost as easy as it comes up!
Here, take a draught of this and you'll be set straight quick.
I don't mind the taste...
Fish, of course. Oh, and here's some jewelry...
Someone said a big boat was coming. Do you see it?
Help has arrived from Limsa! Feast your eyes!
Good gods, would you look at those muscles!
H-Help! Please help!
Hm? Did someone say something?
What in the Fury's name!? H-Hold on!
Are those muscles just a glamour!?
Watch your step, now...
Oh gods, I've got a cramp...
I'll plummet to my death one day...but not today!
Ugh... What did they put in here? \<huff>
I-I thought I was done for! Thank you!
Be more careful, all right?
There's going to be a fountain here.
That sounds delightful, sir!
Oh gods, not again!
I-I'm losing my grip...
That voice... It couldn't be...
Oh, you've got to be kidding me...
Go over each draft at least a dozen times!
Sir, yes, sir!
Now, according to the adventurer's recipe...
Can't stop, won't stop!
The stew certainly has improved.
Where have you been all my life!? \<sob>
Take that! And that!
Concerted works starting soon.
This is it! Let's make it count!
Let's show 'em what we can do.
Yah!
When's the next works starting?
Let's do this!
Any time now. Have to make sure we're fighting fit.
Right behind you!
So the reconstruction finally begins in earnest.
For Ishgaaaaaard! Yaaaaaargh!
We don't need lumber this time. Go and put it back.
Are you sure, miss? I could've sworn...
I must─\<huff>─break you! \<puff>
Concerted works starting soon.
This is it! Let's make it count!
Let's show 'em what we can do.
Yah!
When's the next works starting?
Let's do this!
Any time now. Have to make sure we're fighting fit.
Right behind you!
So the reconstruction finally begins in earnest.
How's it looking?
That's good, clean work.
Looks like it's coming along well.
This fountain is going to be a masterpiece!
Very good, sir!
All credit to the artisans, sir!
You saved me again! How can I ever repay you?
Not falling again would be a start.
I could sculpt all day long!
From devastation to restoration, I must commit all to my mind's eye...
Whew, a rest at last...
Isn't this road just begging for a footrace?
Oh aye, my legs are itching for it!
The Firmament is beginning to take shape!
Bet you can't catch me!
Bet I can!
Bet you can't!
We're waiting on supplies, so rest while you can!
Good work, one and all!
You're only as strong...\<huff>...as your squat!
We work hard, we relax hard!
By the hundredth blow! \<grunt>
Take care not to slip on the rubble!
Watch your footing, now...
Every swing brings us closer to our goal!
Yes, miss!
Aye, sir!
Here's where the dais will be!
These columns need a lot of attention.
Yes, miss!
Sir, yes, sir!
Understood, Chief!
Ugh, my hands are falling asleep...
Make sure we have enough supplies!
Yes, that's the way.
It's all in the details!
Am I doing it right, miss?
Hm, might be a little short...
What to do with this one...
Right, next on the docket...
A fine vantage point for capturing the restoration.
You'll be warm if you keep moving!
Brrr... C-Can't we go somewhere warm?
Gods, but I'm spent...
You need to slow down a little.
Next, we're starting on the residential quarter!
Make sure you're well rested for it.
I feel it! I feel the burn!
Yes! YES! The snows of Coerthas recede before the fire in your thighs!
Yaaaaaargh!
Swing with your entire body, or you'll hurt your arms!
Watch out for flying fragments!
Perhaps you should have a rest...
Do I lift with me knees, or me back?
Suppose we'll be stuck here for a while, then.
You call those squats? I want to see your arse kiss the floor!
How far can we stretch this, I wonder...
If you need supplies, you'll have to speak with Bajsaljen.
Nothing but empty sea.
I have to carry on. My little angel would expect me to.
Ah, blessed warmth...
Such a grand house... It's wasted on me alone.
You're going to fall!
We could ask the residents if they need help?
How about a foray to the Diadem?
I personally could use a rest...
So, what shall we do next?
Grow, my pretties. Grow strong and rise above the cold.
What I need is a family...
That's part of the fun, hee hee!
It's all right, miss! I could do this all day!
Sir, yes, sir!
I will, Chief!
Much better!
Looking good! Keep it up!
Perhaps you should work on a smaller piece...
She may as well be his personal attendant...
It's going to break any moment now, miss! I can feel it!
How's my form, Chief?
Thank you, sir!
Others will take care of the streets. We're looking ahead to the next stage!
The pile of debris needs to go first!
Do we have as many as we should?
From this rubble, a beautiful home will rise!
Let's see...
Yes, sir! I'll check the drafts!
We'll see to it right away, sir!
It's amazing how quickly the Firmament is coming along!
Aye! I can't wait to live here!
Such magnificent images of the Fury!
Stack it there! Take care you don't get your fingers caught!
Are all the blocks in good condition?
Yes, miss! They're as solid as stone!
Aye, sir!
Byregot guide my hand!
Are you all right up there!?
You've brought it all up?
Are you all right!?

The nail that sticks out gets─
OWWW!
Y-Yes, sir... Everything's spinning a little, is all...
Aye, sir!
That should suffice for the sketch.
You've been studying the drafts, I see.
It's starting to take shape! Good!
Is that a crack...?
Each at least a dozen times like you said, sir!
You're too kind, sir!
Bring in materials for the other builders too!
Are you all right!?

I wonder what the kitchen's serv─
OWWW!
Coming along nicely.
That's a lot of supplies.
This is fine material. Handle it with care!
Mmmmmm, smooth...
Yes, sir! We're fortunate to have so many people donating!
Yes, sir! Of course, sir!
Large plot, prime location... Yes, this is absolutely perfect for me.
Bah!
The houses are coming along nicely.
Begging your pardons, but these houses are for war-displaced Ishgardian citizens.
Wait! Who are you? What business have you here?
The end is in sight! Let's stay focused!
Honestly! Pay attention, will you!?

Damn, what's the word for when you─
OWWW!
Yes, Chief!
A masterpiece, even if I do say so myself.
You've improved in leaps and bounds, all of you!
Yes, you may be proud of yourselves!
\<sniff> It's hard to believe we built something so beautiful.
We couldn't have done it without our friends from afar!
There's strength in numbers...and in huge muscles!
This building shall provide affordable housing for many families.
Thank you!
Thank you... (I'll never live this down...)
That was a close call. Be careful next time, both of you.
Behold the beauteous bladework of a Temple Knight!
Feel the irrepressible power of the darkside!
These houses are intended for war-displaced citizens such as your good selves.
Truly? We can live here?
You'll be happy here, I promise.
When she said that she wanted a pet, I thought she had something a little smaller in mind...
N-No! You can't have any of this!
Meowww, meowww!
Meow!
Where's Lord Jannequinard? He should be here by now...
Yes, sir!
Let's review our lessons while we wait!
Today, we shall learn more about the stars and their guidance.
I've brought meals for the workers.
Thank you! I'll see them handed out at once!
Wait, you too?
Me? I have an order for Marcelloix.
\<click> \<click> Let us see what work there is...
If you need repairs, please don't hesitate to let me know.
Thank you kindly!
Uwaaah! Not me this time!? Help! Somebody help!
H-Hold on!
You saved me before! Now it's my turn to save you!
Th-Thank heavens...
Ah, fiddlesticks! I slipped!
Oh, you've got to be kidding me...
Let us take a look. Heh heh heh...
Can you tell me my skyward scores?
What's that man doing?
Looks like he's painting a picture.
Ughhh! I stubbed my bloody toe!

Hello again,
old friend...
...So you visit him still. He would be glad.
Ooh ooh... \<whimper>
I see... You miss your fellows...
Yes, sir! That's very considerate of you, sir!
It's far nicer than I'd dared imagine!
All's well with you and yours?
To be able to live in a warm home... It's a dream come true!
There, there. Sleep now, sweetling.
Right away, sir!
\<slurp> That smells amazing! Can I have a bowl?
My ears are freezing! But that was so much fun!
\<huff> \<huff> Yeah, we've got to do it again!
Many thanks to those who came to our aid.
Just a little further to go...
Dare I say we've seen the last of them?
They were all bathed in Light... Why?
There can be no doubt─'tis indeed the Exarch's magick.
That proved quite a detour, but all's well that ends well.
Play with us, Urianger! Just a little longer!
Why tidy up now when you can do it never?
Have at you!
Yaaah!
Here comes a big one!
Stay sharp!
Try this!
Down with you!
No you don't!
Nothing I can't handle!
Fly true!
Darkness...must be destroyed...
True peace...shall reign...
In the name...of the Light...
Deliverance to all...
Shadow...begone...
How long do you think this'll last?
Who knows? I'll just take it one day at a time.
No matter what happens to this town, we'll always have the view.
You're not getting out of this!
What a mess!
What are we supposed to do now!?
Punishment! Punishment!
You'd better talk fast!
Good work! You've earned an extra lump of coal!
\<beep> Scrap collection complete.
\<beep> Material salvage complete.
Complete? Not yet, it ain't! Go and get some more!
First one to pass out loses!
I'll...show...you!
I've never slept in such a comfy bed...

\<snore>
\<snore>
Good. Now fill up the empty kegs!
I demand to have some booze! More booze, that is.
\<beep> Commencing booze acquisition.
\<beep> Awaiting instructions.
\<beep> Booze acquired.
What I wouldn't give for a swig of grog!
The key to Ronitt's success must be his poses. I'll start with those...
What do you think? Just like Ronitt, eh?
This either makes us look tough, or like we're squatting for another reason entirely.
We're not shirking! This is serious work, I'd have you know!
Yeah! We're the Croaking Bullfrogs, and we wanna be just like Ronitt!
No one messes with Ronitt! That's why he's our role model!
Let me hear you shout!
There you are!
The perfect hiding place...
Where might the others be?
How did you know?
Hee hee! Let's have some fun!
We've been waiting for you!
Now what?
Who the hells are they!?
Ugh, they're strong!
●バトル前２B
There should be no further danger here.
Oi! Where'd you put the thingamabob?
Which thingamabob is that?
The thingamabob with the whatsnames sticking out of it!
Why didn't you say so? It's over there, I think.
The one place I hadn't looked!
Wheels and gears! Gears and wheels!
This way? Or this way?
A tank! More metal for us!
Where to start? Let's see now...
This stone should still serve well...
How do I even begin to repair this?
Take care around the scaffold!
Don't look down... Don't look down...
The new building materials still haven't arrived?
Any moment now, I reckon...
Raaagh!
Gwoooh!
Nobody tosses a dwarf!
Lali, lali, lali-hoooooo!
Did you know Ronitt is the youngest?
How about Karutt and Regitt?
Regitt is three years older than Karutt.
Ozogg is one year younger than Karutt.
Ozogg is five years older than Ronitt. So how many apples does Regitt have?
Please let me work here! I'll do anything!
Anything, you say...?
I want to serve Ishgard in any way I can!
...Very well. But be warned─it's not easy work.
Ah, nothing beats the beach!
All shark and no bite, hah!
Ah, save me! Hold me!
I've been waiting for this day all year!
She's the belle of the beach!
This summer will be even better than the last!
It seems awfully complicated...
The beach is the battlefield today, eh?
Oh, what I wouldn't give to be a dancer too...
If things're lookin' grim, I'll jump to your rescue!
Now where's this so-called monster? I'm sure it's not so tough.
Legs!? It has legs!?
Oh, I just want to snuggle it!
Dance truly is a salve for the soul.
This dance will keep me and mine safe!
The more the merrier!
Not a pixie in sight. Thought they'd play a trick on us by now.
Aye. Wonder where they've all gotten to...
Aye. All I see is that peculiar creature there...
Can't put my finger on it, but something doesn't feel right...
Let's report back for the time being.
We've brought what you asked.
Ooh, let me see! Let me see!
Yes, not a one more or less than requested! Many thanks!
Great. We'll be on our way, then.
Whew, I'm glad that went well.
Aye, get the amount wrong and they'll fair bite your head off...
Well, that was a waste of a trip.
Bah, when they told us we could trade the stones here...
They could've mentioned they don't deal in trifling quantities.
That'll teach us to do our due diligence and check.
Nothing for it but to go and gather some more.
Huzzah, the exit! Safe at last!
My thanks for your kind aid!
Don't mention it. Just glad to be of help.
No, no, I must thank you properly. Come with me to Mord Souq!
We shall have a feast! Yes, a feast with our finest delacies!
Oho, we won't say no to that! Right, Theyler?
Hm, must say I'm curious about the local cuisine...
People made this!? With those fleshy stumps?
They may be fleshy, but they are nimble, and ambitious besides.
The Sea of Clouds! Have you ever been?
What is your home called?
Wait... Where am I?
I've come to give my regards to Ehll Tou, but I seem to have lost my way...
Many thanks! It's so easy to lose your way here.
Maybe I can help. Who are you looking for?
Ah, I know her! Everyone around here does. Climb these stairs and you should spot her before long.
There shouldn't be any sharks on these shores, especially not so close...
The next big win is mine, I can feel it!
My “Dawn Deck” will be unstoppable!
Prepare to feel my fist of rage!
Oh, calm down, Ulala...
You've the worst mahjong face, my friend...
Hmm, what should I do now...?
\<gasp> The size of this place!
Where shall we start!?
Just one more try...
What, again!?
There's a time for soldierin' and there's a time for loafin'.
Take care not to spend too much time in the sun.
We simply must introduce this dance in Coerthas, if only to bring a mote of summer's warmth with us.
So this is what an eternal summer feels like...
I've never felt more alive!
Good luck getting me to leave!
It's so hot... Perhaps if I doffed my armor...
Come on, get in the water!
I don't ever want this celebration to end...
Do you hear me!? I don't want to see a one of you slacking!
My arm feels like it's about to fall off...
Let's do this!
Leave it to me.
I'll do the heavy lifting!
Take that! And that!
Steady the hips...and swing!
Yes, this is quite an inspiring scene.
Just look at those bulging biceps...
Keep at that same spot!
Not half bad, I say.
My sides are achin' somethin' fierce...
How's it lookin'?
You got it, Chief!
Ungh!
Finally figured out how to use that pickaxe, I see.
How about you try your hand with a hammer next?
Aye aye, Chief!
Thank ye kindly!
Pound! Smash! Crash!
